the static equation of motion of open p-adic string theory, which we
know admits Gaussian lump solutions
. We thus interpret these
solutions as lower dimensional D-branes living in flat spacetime.
By flat spacetime we mean more precisely that the closed string tachyon 
is in its perturbative vacuum. 

We now want to consider nontrivial static configurations of . We
readily see that () looks very much like the static
